title.rendered: VLT Aqua Drive FC 202 product training for key customers

content.rendered: Together with partners Danfoss, TTE Trading hosted a customer event to showcase the VLT Aqua Drive FC 202, a cost efficient and high performing VLT drive that uses Condition-Based Monitoring and is known for its energy efficiency and optimum asset protection. Experts from the panel building community and water treatment industry joined for a highly interactive knowledge sharing session. Khurram Shahzad and Jai Masand, product experts from Danfoss introduced the VLT Aqua FC 202 Series to the industry professionals, during the highly interactive session.
